HEADWORD: Mezza voce
<hw>Mez"za vo"ce</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[It., fr. <ets>mezzo</ets>,
fem. <ets>mezza</ets> middle, half + <ets>voce</ets> voice, L.
<ets>vox</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Mus.)</fld> <def>With a medium fullness of
